value: scent bottle, in form of Taweret-Sekhmet-Sobek composite deity. The bottle exhibits the pregnant hippo form of Taweret with an incised beard under the chin representing the leonine goddess, Sekhmet. The god Sobek is represented as a crocodile on the back of the hippo.
Diorite bottle in the form of Taweret-Sekhmet-Sobek
